  Memories
  Choose how Codewith uses and creates memories. Changes are saved to config.t

› [x] Use memories       Use memories in the following threads. Applied at
                         next thread.
  [ ] Generate memories  Generate memories from the following threads. Current
                         thread included.
  Reset all memories     Clear local memory files and summaries. Existing
                         threads stay intact.

  Learn more: https://github.com/hasna/codewith/blob/main/docs/config.md

  Press space to toggle; enter to save or select
